tips.text: Great patio outside for those who enjoy fresh air with urban Downtown LA skyline. Order the Quesadilla!

formattedAddress: 2100 E Cesar E Chavez Ave (at N St Louis St)

tips.text: You can pay a buck & get a little packet of chiles torreados as a side, or you can get them as a taco wrapped in a thick corn tortilla with Guisados’ liquid habanero chile salsa on top -Jonathan Gold
Get the sampler!  They tell me they are BYOB until they get their alcohol permit.🍻
TORTA TORTA TORTA!!! with pastor or carne asada

tips.text: The branzino is soooo good! Chips and guac, corn on a cob and the lobster taco🍴😋
The best of the King Tacos.  Carne asada burrito with green sauce and the al pastor tacos...extra green sauce on the side!
Tilapia tacos and jimmy taco are bomb.
Featured at the First Annual LA Weekly Tacolandia! Look for the truck in the downtown area or flag it down in East LA!

tips.text: The tacos were fantastic! Chicharron Tacos are the best!
